"啟動開發人員模式後，按一下 :guilabel:`編輯範圍` （若可用），然後"
"按 :guilabel:`新增規則`。"

#: ../../content/applications/studio/automated_actions.rst:92
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Apply on` domain defines the conditions a record must meet "
